hadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/four-rakaat-dhuhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":36421,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Four raka\u2019at before Dhuhur ascend to heaven","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray four cycles before noon prayer. It was said to him, \u201cYou are always performing this prayer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, gates of heavens are opened when the sun begins to decline. They do not begin to close\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28899,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/taraweeh-prayer-in-ramadan-rakaat\/","url_meta":{"origin":36421,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tarawih: The Prophet\u2019s night prayer in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salamah reported: He asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cHow was the night prayer of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, during Ramadan?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cHe would not pray more than eleven cycles in Ramadan or other times. He would pray four cycles,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyh